data.description: Like New!!! Huge almost 3600 Sq Ft 4 Bedroom 2.5 Bath home on a Cul de Sac lot that is only 7 years old!!!  Awesome Kitchen with Granite Counters, Large island, upgraded cabinets, Stainless appliances & walk in pantry.  Spacious Main bedroom suite with Trey ceiling, 2 walk in closets, Tile shower, Garden tub & Double sinks. 2 way Fireplace between extra large Great Room & Breakfast Nook. Separate Den & Dining rooms are also on the main floor and there is a nice loft area upstairs too. Cul de Sac lot backs up to common area and offers some extra privacy. Also, all appliances remain with this wonderful home!!
